<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fool-seal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5682922); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5682922&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="Fool Seal" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5682922)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/fool-seal" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5682922); return false;">Fool Seal</a></span>：</strong>呃这篇是不是没有评论最好（huaji</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6150792&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="HigashikataJosuke" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6150792)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/higashikatajosuke" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6150792); return false;">HigashikataJosuke</a></span>：</strong>真就个<strong>逆模因</strong>帖子呗</p>
