</div>
</div>
<p>20██/██/██ ██:██, 地点：Site-CN-05</p>
<hr />
<p>听说总部的SCP-682因为酒驾撞在树上死了。</p>
<p>额&#8230;抱歉，我只有二级权限。阅读SCP-682的文档需要三级权限。所以我不知道你在说什么。</p>
<hr />
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">+&nbsp;评论区&nbsp;4个</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded-link"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">-&nbsp;评论区</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-content">
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6159447&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="JosephJoestar" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6159447)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/josephjoestar" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6159447); return false;">JosephJoestar</a></span>：<span style="color: green">草</span></strong></p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ploplo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6286770); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6286770&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="ploplo" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6286770)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ploplo" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6286770); return false;">ploplo</a></span>：</strong>梦幻联动啊草</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c8h17oh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5420288); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5420288&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="C8H17OH" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5420288)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/c8h17oh" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5420288); return false;">C8H17OH</a></span>：</strong><span style="text-decoration: line-through;">有一点小问题：在世界观内应该称呼为“总部”而非“主站”（又不是只有一个站）。不过还是</span>蛮有趣的，up了。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-destroyerplantard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6516148); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6516148&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203009" alt="Dr DestroyerPlantard" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6516148)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/dr-destroyerplantard" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6516148); return false;">Dr DestroyerPlantard</a></span>：</strong>我把“Site cn-05”改成了“Site-CN-05”。挺好的，UP了。</p>
</blockquote>
