<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jwhdetd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6330489); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6330489&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203010" alt="JWHDETD" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6330489)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/jwhdetd" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6330489); return false;">JWHDETD</a></span>：</strong>同感，云小鬼确实令人不怎么好受</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/durot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3164731); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3164731&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203010" alt="Durot" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3164731)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/durot" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3164731); return false;">Durot</a></span>：</strong>虽然但是，我觉得这篇至少应该存在（</p>
