<hr />
<p><iframe src="/short-stories:00083/html/735f25ce9cda9046f90d643c70806c9cf3ebbd0a-7249941551827056981" allowtransparency="true" frameborder="0" class="html-block-iframe"></iframe></p>
<hr />
<p>好困&#8230;&#8230;不行，我必须赶完这篇scp&#8230;&#8230;</p>
<p>嗯&#8230;&#8230;好的，多谢&#8230;&#8230;..！卧槽，是谁，刚才给我烟的<a href="/scp-4999">西装男</a>是谁？</p>
<p>&#8230;还好，转头四处看去<a href="/nobody-hub">没有人</a>在旁边，欸，困得迷糊了&#8230;&#8230;.再不睡就猝死了&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
<p>不行&#8230;&#8230;.</p>
<hr />
