<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4055881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203010" alt="Etinjat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4055881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;">Etinjat</a></span>：</strong>从归档处转来</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6357357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203010" alt="Macro Z" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6357357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;">Macro Z</a></span>：</strong>啊…这，守望我等之人。</p>
</blockquote>
<blockquote>
<p><strong><span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=6357357&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1610203010" alt="Macro Z" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=6357357)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/macro-z" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(6357357); return false;">Macro Z</a></span>：</strong>今天10月四号，凌晨三点二十七，百无聊赖的我不知为何来到了这个页面，看见了标题。</p>
